  "content_id": "71f0d7e3-23d7-45ef-a7f0-08f221473d0c",
  "description": "Help by giving your money, time and skills if there's been a natural disaster or humanitarian emergency overseas",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You can donate money to aid organisations and agencies, or volunteer your time and skills if there’s been a natural disaster or humanitarian emergency overseas.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"donations\">Donations</h2>\n\n<p>Donate through the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.dec.org.uk/\">Disasters Emergency Committee (<abbr title=\"Disasters Emergency Committee\">DEC</abbr>)</a>. This will make sure your donation reaches those most in need.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Do not send food or clothing directly to an affected area, because you could delay supplies reaching those most in need.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"volunteering\">Volunteering</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"in-the-uk\">In the UK</h3>\n\n<p>You can help by volunteering to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>organise a fundraising event</li>\n  <li>staff a phone line for an aid agency</li>\n  <li>work in a charity shop</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"in-the-disaster-affected-area\">In the disaster-affected area</h3>\n\n<p>You can register with a disaster relief charity such as <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.redr.org.uk\">RedR</a> if you have specific skills that can help, for example:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>engineering</li>\n  <li>health</li>\n  <li>child protection</li>\n  <li>logistics</li>\n  <li>search and rescue</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>Do not travel to a disaster-affected area unless you’re working with an aid agency.</p>\n</div>\n\n",
